{"type": "article", "id": 8680, "title": "咖啡工具套装", "description": "", "date": "2015-04-20T07:28:57Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 4, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605235320ZVdNgk2sWaUhxOLz.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t日本咖啡公司为了庆祝其一周年，联手 Head Porter 推出了一个咖啡工具套装系列，包含 Espresso Set，Dripper Set 和 Professional Kit 三种款式可以选择， 外观上采用了 Head Porter 经典款造型，内部配备了 Bialetti 加热水壶，杯子，研磨机，围裙，温度计等。点击 <a href=\"http://www.toriba-coffee.com/\" target=\"_blank\">Toriba 官方主页</a>可以查看更多信息。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235318KgszbWeIcFDVyhZA.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235318GJIf0apgeyj78inD.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235319KGFq1ZtphjxQrROn.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235319fwXZn6ScQEWBkMzJ.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235320v5RT8dbjCwgzUDFJ.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n"}